<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">No actions are required unless the print quality is out of specification</b>. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-AC47A052-306F-4816-90C4-8607D0058A9D" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
