<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Calibration step</u> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This warning is generated during the calibration step: "PrintheadPAINtReference" which is part of the printhead calibration sequence. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Patterns in calibration print</u> 
